description: First up, tall, lanky SKY DEVIL tops slinged-up MATTHIEU PARIS inan elbow-deep power-plowing that brings out the bloom inMATTHIEU's famous rose bud. MATTHIEU keeps ordering SKY togive him more and more. SKY is only too eager to accommodate,easily fitting both of his large paddle hands into MATTHIEU's gapinghole.
title: Fistpack 21 - All Hands On Deck, Scene #01
